                     <content styleCode="bold">﻿Inactive ingredients</content>
                  </content>
               </title>
               <text>
                  <paragraph>Water, Propylene Glycol, Achillea Millefolium (Yarrow) Extract, Yucca Glauca Root Extract, Citric Acid, Sodium Metabisulfate, Caprylyl Glycol, Disodium EDTA, Methylisothiazolinone.</paragraph>
               </text>
               <effectiveTime value="20121003"/>
            </section>
